data.description: San Diegans battling human trafficking for sex and labor were recognized Nov. 27, at La Mesa Soroptimist’s 62nd annual pre-Thanksgiving community breakfast at the Handlery Hotel.
data.title: Soroptimists honor fighters against human trafficking
